rest_of_day_open: Hopefully at least okay, It's suppose to be fourth of july weekend festivities but everything is cancelled due to covid.  I think that Texas will close down again and that this will impact me and my regular work hours. I want it to go well, I want coronavirus to go away.
critical_positive: I think that my conversation partner was good at talking and that he could easily hear me.  He was also understanding. critical_negative: I think I was a bit nervous and jittery at the beginning as I've been a little jittery these past few days.
